data.title: FRINGE star ANNA TORV returns from Comic-Con
data.meta_description: Since Fringe has come to Vancouver, I have had the luck to have met practically all of the primary cast.....except 1. Anna Torv. Yesterday, that changed finally. Anna returned from the Comic-Con in...
data.text:
Since Fringe has come to Vancouver, I have had the luck to have met practically all of the primary cast.....except 1. Anna Torv.

Yesterday, that changed finally.

Anna returned from the Comic-Con in San Diego, and we were there to meet her. She was prime objective #1 for everyone. Mostly, because no one had yet to get her since she got her.

She came thru the doors, and the hounds & fans were waiting eagerly. She stopped to sign for a minute or two & even chatted breifly with a couple of people.

With Anna out of the way now, the only notable cast members I havent gotten yet, are 2 that I dont think will be back (Kirk Acevedo & Mark Valley) from what I have heard & The Observer (Michael Cerveris).
